# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Released]
## [2.1.0] - 11-12-2022
### Changed
- Refactory web (change GUI and upgrade nuxt2 to nuxt3)

## [2.0.0] - 08-08-2022
### Added
- room virtual for watch video with friends
- ConversionSerivce for convert file ts to mp4 for streaming
- Websocket for change information for streaming
- Http-server for expose files video for streaming
- docker-compose-unstable (get image beta)

### Fixed
- resolve bug for get url mp4 by html

### Changed
- file docker-compose

## [1.0.1] - 20-07-2022
### Fixed
- resolve size button of mangaworld for mobile
- resolve crash upgradeService
- change domain for anime

### Changed
- update interfaces for back end

## [1.0.0] - 23-05-2022
### Added
- now support Manga (use mangaworld)

### Changed
- Banner
- Structure DB

### Fixed
- Problem refresh when delete anime/manga
- Disable autoset season for anime

## [0.3.2] - 21-04-2022
### Fixed
- order list when add new episodes how notify
- resolve problem performance of the cpu always at 100%

## [0.3.1] - 20-04-2022
### Changed
- Now use nuget of Discord Webhook

### Add
- Support parallel now with UpdateService
- Now for notify add new Anime/Episode is incluse with image 

### Fixed
- Clear code
- Resolve order list of the episodes in web
- Improve parallel
- Improve interface web general

## [0.3.0] - 17-04-2022
### Added
- Now you can delete anime (only in db!)
- Now recive also notify of when add new anime and remove old anime

### Changed
- change color for download anime (now is yellow)

### Fixed
- Refactory code c#
- Problem check already downloaded anime with bar search to animeSaturn

### Bug
- Resolve problem method Hash when open file busy
- DownloadService delete messages duplicated

## [0.2.5] - 10-04-2022
### Fixed
- Resolve problem show disk space

## [0.2.4] - 10-04-2022
### Fixed
- Resolve problem get urls for episodes during download in parallel
- UpdateService also update the renaming of a file

### Add
- Show information space disk
- Show information health of services
- Add slide bar for see informations

## [0.2.3] - 08-04-2022
### Add
- Webhook Discord for log

### Fixed
- Module HtmlAnimeSaturn now work in parallel for download urls of episodes
- Module Download now work in parallel for second method (use with buffers) of episodes
- Fixed overflow memory when calculate hash of one episode over 1GB size

## [0.2.2] - 06-04-2022
### Add
- Setup default environment global

### Fixed
- Change structure for logger

## [0.2.1] - 05-04-2022
### Add
- Notify service that send messages to Discord with Webhook

### Fixed
- Add environment logger for reduced lines of log

## [0.2.0] - 01-04-2022
### Add
- Tracking files and movements (modified class models and added new table)
- Check Hash256
- Browser support now Mobile
- Add all description of an anime into card, if anime not already downloaded show a link for redirect original page with information

### Fixed
- Improve call API
- Improve conversion class model to class dto or reverse
- If Anime already downloaded not show button for download episodes

### Changed
- Split two part of UpdateService, UpdateService check integry files on local and UpgradeService check new or missing episodes into db
- Buttons Search
- Size pagination
- replace 'previous' and 'next' with arrows in pagination
- Show status of downloads after press a button


## [0.1.2] - 29-03-2022
### Add
- Add button re-download anime if download are stop

### Fixed
- when download is filed, bar progress is red with write 'filed' instead of percentual with value 100%
- when download is completed, bar progress is green with write 'completed' instead of percentual
- Resolve problem open file

### Changed
- DownloadService start timeout 0 to max limit defined and print log if error download with attempts remains, if download is success reset timeout

## [0.1.1] - 29-03-2022
### Added
- new button into bar search for get all anime

### Changed
- color buttons into bar search


## [0.1.0] - 27-03-2022
### Version Stable